headline: Healthpeak Properties Announces $925 Million of Transaction Activity
summary: DENVER, January 12, 2026--Healthpeak Properties, Inc. (NYSE: DOC), a leading owner, operator, and developer of real estate for healthcare discovery and delivery, today announced recent transaction activity totaling approximately $925 million, reflecting continued execution on the Company’s capital allocation strategy.
